						<div class="sec_inner1 sec_inner">
							<div class="sec_txt">
								<p class="txt1">Growing together and sharing<br>performance lay the root<br>for sustainability.</p>
								<p class="txt2">Growing together is a continuous process of discovering challenges and taking actions rather than pursuing a certain goal.  SM Group is actively reflecting various internal/external ideas and systems for growth together to create a culture of coexistence and cooperation for the abundance of all families of SM.</p>
							</div>
							<div class="sec_tit" data-motion="scaleType1">
								<div class="img_box"><img src="/resource/eng/mobile/images/sustainability/partnership/view_sec1_img1.jpg" alt=""></div>
							</div>
