								<h3 data-role="m_elm">Roadmap 3 Steps</h3>
								<ol class="roadmap_lst">
									<li data-role="m_elm"><strong>Design</strong><span>Exploring challenges and developing<br>systems to grow together.</span></li>
									<li data-role="m_elm"><strong>Putting systems in place<br>to grow together</strong><span>Building strong collaborative systems<br>for shared growth.</span></li>
									<li data-role="m_elm"><strong>Achieving shared growth</strong><span>Realizing values and sharing performance for growth of entire organization.</span></li>
								</ol>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="sec2 section">
					<span id="page2" class="anchor"></span>
					<div class="anchor_wrap">
						<div class="sec_inner1 sec_inner">
							<div class="sec_txt">
								<p class="txt1">Beautiful partnerships support<br>pride and competitiveness.</p>
								<p class="txt2">SM Group will take initiatives for all families of SM to achieve the highest level of quality through ceaseless efforts for coexistence and development.  We will create beautiful partnerships so the achievements we make together bring pride to all families of SM and being a member of SM becomes the symbol of competitiveness.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="sec_inner2 sec_inner" data-motion="bgType1"  data-trigger="slide">
							<div class="inner">
								<div class="right">
									<h3>Our Goal</h3>
									<div class="slide_wrap programs">
										<div class="slide_cont swiper-wrapper">
											<div class="slide swiper-slide">
												<dl>
													<dt>We will build partnerships of reliability and trust based on transparency and fairness.</dt>
													<dd>We will improve capacities and qualities as the leader of growth together and establish fair trade based on the transparency of ethical management.</dd>
												</dl>
											</div>
											<div class="slide swiper-slide">
												<dl>
													<dt>We will communicate and cooperate with partners ceaselessly for better outcomes.</dt>
													<dd>We will improve communication by remaining active and involved. We will schedule regular gatherings and conduct satisfaction surveys for better partnerships.</dd>
												</dl>
											</div>
											<div class="slide swiper-slide">
												<dl>
													<dt>We will secure support for competitiveness.</dt>
													<dd>We will share knowhow and resources in various areas, including construction, manufacture, seaborne transportation, and services, for our partners to achieve higher level of quality and competitiveness.</dd>
												</dl>
											</div>
										</div>
