					<div class="anchor_wrap">
						<div class="sec_inner1 sec_inner">
							<div class="sec_txt">
								<p class="txt1">The principle of management is to earn respect by fulfilling social responsibilities through management of satisfaction and coexistence.</p>
								<p class="txt2">SM Group will not just shout for coexistence and growth together. As an old saint said, “Encounters should be valued and relationships should be beautiful“ SM Group will make ceaseless efforts so we can share precious relationships with partners for a long time. Based on the principle that competitive partners give us competitiveness, SM Group will lay the foundation for growth together.</p>
							</div>
							<div class="sec_tit" data-motion="scaleType1">
								<div class="img_box"><img src="/resource/eng/mobile/images/sustainability/partnership/view_sec3_img1.jpg" alt=""></div>
								<ul class="ldeology_lst" data-motion="staggerType1">
									<li data-role="m_elm">· Establishing fair trade orders</li>
									<li data-role="m_elm">· Support for win-win partnerships</li>
									<li data-role="m_elm">· Communication with partners</li>
									<li data-role="m_elm">· Ethical management with<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;transparency</li>
								</ul>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
