					<span id="page4" class="anchor"></span>
					<div class="anchor_wrap">
						<div class="sec_inner1 sec_inner">
							<div class="inner">
								<div class="sec_txt">
									<p class="txt1">We share the hope and fruit of<br>tomorrow with all partners.</p>
									<p class="txt2">SM Group has suggested a blueprint for the construction division and declared growth together through various year-round campaigns for ‘safety’ and partner comments. We are actively gathering partner comments for technical competitiveness, productivity, and cost-saving ideas and listening to complaints for coexistence and growth together.</p>
								</div>
								<div class="sec_tit" data-motion="scaleType1">
									<div class="img_box"><img src="/resource/eng/mobile/images/sustainability/partnership/view_sec4_img1.jpg" alt=""></div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
